data.description: This charming renovated home boasts a delightful blend of modern amenities and timeless upgrades! The interior showcases a fresh, open layout with gleaming hardwood floors and a stylish kitchen adorned with quartz countertops and enhanced appliances. Sunlit rooms feature cozy nooks and delightful touches, while the updated bathrooms showcase contemporary fixtures. Enjoy the convenience of a new roof (2018) and revel in the adorable charm that permeates every corner of this inviting residence. $6000 seller credit with an acceptable offer! Your dream home awaits!
